{"tid":1150213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好奇大陸法官係咩出身先咁騎呢","createTime":"2019-05-11T16:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T17:06:10.000Z","uid":57346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0ec3ac0ee55be61d4d7ccc7e86f8c5dc50c017","tid":1150213,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"但google左一陣見到篇咁既野，想開個天涯acc去屌9佢地！<br />\n<br />\n不過註冊極都搞唔到！<br />\n<br />\n我睇到有d嬲！大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nkeerte <br />\n2017-03-30 08:36<br />\n既然香港的大陆允许外国人当法官，那么大陆人是否也可以呢？香港人肯定是可以的，这个不用讨论了，现在问题就是外国人都可以，咱大陆人是否可以做香港的法官？如果可以的话，建议中央派遣一批法官对香港进行法律援助嘛。既然香港人这么笨，连个法官都没有人能做，那就让法律地区法官来干好了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-worldlook-1773390-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tianya.cn%2Fm%2Fpost-worldlook-1773390-1.shtml&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=c4083937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-worldlook-1773390-1.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"36cbaa6da971eb9811c448f108da23c3f88b0386","tid":1150213,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"民智未開既國家屌黎都曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0281d0fc4986508b4897c88c94083cefc6c3baf1","tid":1150213,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20160309-mainland-judge-aboutme/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20160309-mainland-judge-aboutme%2F&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=69b81573\" target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20160309-mainland-judge-aboutme/</a><br />\n大陸法官自畫像：「賺白菜的錢，操白粉的心」<br />\n忙碌，沒有尊嚴，經濟沒有保障，晉升沒有空間。大陸的法官們自稱是這樣一類人：司法民工。"}]}